[SHORT DESC]
All active Pokémon faint after 3 turns.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>All Pokémon on the field faint after 3 turns. Even Pokémon that are in the invulnerable stage of Dig and Fly are affected. The effect is removed by switching; however, the effect is passed onto a teammate if the target uses Baton Pass.</p>